rom hyperfine structure seen in\nthe Ba II resonance line lambda4554. Based on these data we deduce for the\nthick disk stars the ratio of the s/r-process contribution to barium as 30 : 70\n(+- 30%), in agreement with the results obtained from the [Eu/Ba] ratios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Oct 2002 14:48:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
